{"tid":1111620,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【安心偷食】與黃心穎同屆！張名雅支持Sammi：知道是錯選擇犯錯","createTime":"2019-04-17T03:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T04:17:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9b8ed8987ed270b600b7486c406bf56c2610ffd6","tid":1111620,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:44:38.000Z","msg":"昨日《蘋果》獨家爆黃心穎及許志安在車廂後座攬啜拖的片段，全城轟動，網民心痛Sammi被蒙在鼓裡、馬國明慘變綠帽俠兼轉揸「降魔綠的」，⁣黃心穎雖然未現身，但她的IG禁留言，令網民湧至與黃心穎撞樣的蔡一智IG洗版罵爆，網上謠傳越來⁣越多，直至昨晚7時多，許志安憔悴開記招，爆喊承認自己起色心，稱「我係一個壞嘅人」，公開向Sammi及其家人道歉（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IBZjL5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IBZjL5&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=dced1b37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IBZjL5</a> ），經理人黃柏高Paco發聲明指安仔一時糊塗，「希望Sammi畀次機會佢」。<br />\n與心穎同屆的港姐張名雅在IG留言：「呢個世界實在太多誘惑。大家都知道是錯的，但都會選擇犯錯。Mi，你要加油，活得更好。」已為人妻的張名雅選擇幫理不幫親，支持同是教友的Sammi；同時有網民批評無綫應該取消黃心穎《2012年度香港小姐競選》亞軍資格。<br />\n此外，有報道指無綫認為「安心偷食」事件，令黃心穎形象盡毀，決定即時「雪藏」黃心穎，而高層樂易玲只透露關心及擔心馬國明，對黃心穎隻字不提。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190417/large/1555471590_4e97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190417%2Flarge%2F1555471590_4e97.jpg&h=cefe682e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190417/59497858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190417%2F59497858&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=b6442844\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190417%2F59497858&h=607b3f0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190417/59497858</a>"},{"pid":"9e76a53086383f8bb7ef22a5415d3ca07b6eb00a","tid":1111620,"uid":197640,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201